		<title>ITauthor podcast #16 – Flare and Chrome, the pubcast</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/itauthor/~3/OILb-7vd54c/</link>
		<comments>http://www.itauthor.com/2008/09/20/itauthor-podcast-16-flare-and-chrome-the-pubcast/#comments</comments>
