		<title>ITauthor podcast #8 – May 19th, 2007 – The Dogcast</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/itauthor/~3/doQvdufFR-s/</link>
		<comments>http://www.itauthor.com/2007/05/20/itauthor-podcast-8-may-19th-2007/#comments</comments>
